# View Tax Logs in System Health

Learn how to navigate the Tax Dashboard in System Health to review logs and handle errors effectively.

Navigate to the Tax Dashboard under System Health to review request and response logs from your new tax engine.

![Tax Dashboard System Health](https://zuora.deploy.heretto.com/v4/deployments/QPAZk6lsgXwvotedNERE/object/e2590ba0-be48-42b7-bab9-4a9ec3111cad?jwt=eyJ0eXAiOiJKV1QiLCJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9..llTE2Dgz4phbnA5uewscBkIYwuPHL7OMTRJyyCWcfyA)

Zuora will display the error message returned by Anrok. For more details, including the error description and how to resolve it, visit the [Anrok website](https://apidocs.anrok.com/tutorials/faq#how-should-i-handle-errors).
